<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Make known to me your ways, Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">teach me your paths.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Guide me into your truth and teach me,</para>

<para style="q1">for you are the God of my salvation;</para>

<para style="q1">I hope in you all day long.</para>
